Insider Activity


Individual




Dominic J. Pileggi



Mr. Dominic J. Pileggi is Independent Director at Acuity Brands, Inc. and a Member at The Council on Competitiveness. He is on the Board of Directors at Acuity Brands, Inc., Viasystems, Inc., and Omni Cable Corp.
Mr. Pileggi was previously employed as Independent Director by Viasystems Group, Inc., Independent Director by Exide Technologies, Inc., Lead Director by The Lubrizol Corp., Chairman by Thomas & Betts Tennessee, Inc., President-Electro Mechanical Solutions Division by Viasystems Group, Inc., President-Electro Mechanical Solutions Division by Viasystems, Inc., President & Chief Executive Officer by Jordan Telecommunication Products, Inc., President & Chief Executive Officer by Casco Plastics, Inc., President-Electrical Products Group by Thomas & Betts Tennessee, Inc., and Chairman by National Electrical Manufacturers Association. He also served on the board at Exide Corp.
He received his undergraduate degree from Rutgers University (New Jersey).



